Retrouvez sur cette chaîne les bandes-annonces de vos séries et films Netflix préférés (sous-titrés et/ou doublés en français parce qu’ici on est en France messieurs, dames et en France (attention info exclusive) ON PARLE FRANÇAIS), mais aussi des récapitulatifs (entre nous, on a tous une mémoire un peu courte, soyons honnêtes), des vidéos exclusives avec vos acteurs et actrices favoris mais pas que ! snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS SEASON 5 TRAILER (2025) | Netflix
snippet.description:
#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Stranger Things returns for its most intense chapter yet in this fan-made concept trailer for Stranger Things Season 5. Featuring characters like Eleven, Will Byers, Mike Wheeler, Dustin, Lucas, Max, Jonathan Byers, Joyce Byers, Steve Harrington, and Chief Hopper, this trailer imagines the final battle against Vecna. Inspired by Netflix’s official tone and the epic energy of the Stranger Things 5 Final Season Trailer 2, this edit aims to capture the drama, tension, and emotional stakes of the show’s last season.

The inspiration behind this video:
Prepare for the beginning of the end with the Stranger Things Season 5 Trailer, the highly anticipated look at the Stranger Things 5 Final Season trailer 2. As Netflix gears up for the massive conclusion of its flagship series, we break down every secret hidden in the Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser. Whether you are searching for the stranger things season 5 volume 2 trailer, the stranger things 5 trailer, or updates on stranger things season 5 part 2, this video covers it all. The st5 trailer teases an apocalyptic showdown, and our analysis of the stranger things final trailer explores how the saga will close.

The stakes have never been higher as Vecna (played by Jamie Campbell Bower) threatens to destroy the world, forcing Eleven (Millie Bobby Brown) to make the ultimate sacrifice. In this breakdown of the stranger things 5 volume 2 trailer, we explore the fates of Max (Sadie Sink), Lucas (Caleb McLaughlin), Dustin (Gaten Matarazzo), and Will Byers (Noah Schnapp). We also dive into the arcs for Chief Hopper (David Harbour), Joyce Byers (Winona Ryder), Mike Wheeler (Finn Wolfhard), and the older teens including Steve Harrington (Joe Keery), Maya Hawke, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, and Cara Buono. Every frame of the stranger things season 5 part 2 trailer hints at who lives and who dies.

If you enjoy high-quality trailer coverage from channels like Rotten Tomatoes TV, Teaser PRO, FilmSpot Trailer, MovieGasm, KinoCheck, EmergencyAwesome, and IGN TV Trailer, you are in the right place. We bring you the latest tv promos and deep dives into the stranger things 5 vol 2 trailer and stranger things 5 trailer volume 2. Join the conversation about Stranger Things Season 5 and Stranger Things 5 as we wait for the final episodes to drop on Netflix. Don't forget to like and subscribe for more updates on the Stranger Things trailer and the epic finale!

snippet.title: The God Slayer - Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy this nine-minute gameplay reveal trailer for The God Slayer, the upcoming open-world steampunk fantasy RPG from Pathea Games, creators of the My Time series. It's in development for PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X|S. 

The developers describe The God Slayer as follows: "Enter an Eastern-inspired steampunk metropolis where gods known as Celestials reign with a divine fist! In this premium open-world RPG, you are an Elemancer who refuses to bow to his creators. Infused with elemental powers and a heart of vengeance, you will dethrone them all. You will rise to be The God Slayer."

Wishlist The God Slayer on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2536510/

snippet.title: READY OR NOT 2: HERE I COME | Official Trailer | Searchlight Pictures
snippet.description:
Moments after surviving an all-out attack from the Le Domas family, Grace (Samara Weaving) discovers she’s reached the next level of the nightmarish game — and this time with her estranged sister Faith (Kathryn Newton) at her side. Grace has one chance to survive, keep her sister alive, and claim the High Seat of the Council that controls the world. Four rival families are hunting her for the throne, and whoever wins rules it all.

Directed by: Matt Bettinelli-Olpin & Tyler Gillett
Written & Directed by: Guy Busick & R. Christopher Murphy

snippet.title: 28 ANS PLUS TARD : Le Temple Des Morts Bande Annonce VF (2026) Nouvelle
snippet.description:
Dans ce nouveau volet de la saga, le docteur Kelson noue une relation aussi troublante qu’inattendue dont les répercussions sont susceptibles de bouleverser notre monde. De l’autre côté, la rencontre entre Spike et Jimmy Crystal tourne au cauchemar. Dans LE TEMPLE DES MORTS, ce ne sont plus les infectés qui représentent la plus grande menace pour la survie de l’espèce humaine – c’est l’absence d’humanité des rescapés qui se révèle être le danger le plus terrifiant…

About SlisTeaser:
SlisTeaser create trailer mashups—also known as recut trailers—by combining scenes from one or more movies to craft new, imaginative trailers.
These fan-made edits often reimagine a film’s genre or storyline, offering a fresh perspective on familiar footage.
Due to their transformative nature, these mashups are protected under Fair Use as parody, adding creative spin and anticipation for fans and upcoming releases.

snippet.title: Guild Wars Reforged Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A Legend Reforged | Play with No Subscription Fee

Experience Guild Wars Reforged: The award-winning online roleplaying game enjoyed by millions, now re-energized with system enhancements. From the fall of Ascalon to the desperate stand against Nightfall—every campaign is a chapter in Tyriaʼs epic history. Your adventure is just getting started!

New Features:

•Free to existing Guild Wars owners!
•New bundled low price for new players including Prophecies, Factions, and Nightfall 
•Steam Deck Verified (Pending)
•Support for XInput controllers (such as the Xbox Wireless Controller)
•New quest tracking and direction system
•On-screen control guide
•UI enhanced with HD skill icons, larger text options, and quality-of-life improvements
•Support for high DPI displays
•New ambient occlusion, HD bloom, and antialiasing rendering enhancements
•Rebuilt audio system with environmental effects (no hardware support needed)

For more information and to purchase, head over to:  https://www.guildwars.com/

snippet.title: Le clip Reggae qui fait réfléchir : Vis, Ris, Aime. Parce que tout passe !

PARCE QUE TOUT PASSE – Rap Game IA | Clip officiel roots reggae introspectif. Roots reggae introspectif, chanson sur le temps qui passe, nostalgie, enfance, vie qui file, clip émotionnel Rap Game IA, reggae poétique, introspection, lumière, souvenirs, sagesse. Laisse-toi porter par “Parce que tout passe”, un morceau qui déroule une vie entière comme un film. De l’enfance innocente aux années qui s’empilent trop vite, des rêves qu’on poursuit aux regrets qu’on dépose… ce clip raconte ce qu’on vit tous. Parce qu’au final… on ne retient rien, sauf l’amour. snippet.title: Flea - A Plea (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Flea's "A Plea" is out now on Nonesuch Records: https://flea.lnk.to/APlea 

Flea — Electric Bass, Vocals and Trumpet 

Anna Butterss — Upright Bass, Vocals 
Deantoni Parks — Drums, Vocals 
Jeff Parker — Guitar, Vocals 
Mauro Refosco — Percussion 
Rickey Washington — Alto Flute 
Vikram Devasthali — Trombone 
Chris Warren — Vocals 
Josh Johnson — Alto Saxophone, Vocals 

Directed By: Clara Balzary 
Produced By: Corrine Dye 
Production Company: First Matter 
Cinematography By: Jimmy Nyeango 
Choreography By: Sadie Wilking 
Edited By: Sid Williams 

1st AD: Lewis Rangal 
1st AC: Govinda Angulo 
Camera A - Gimbal Operator: Jason Robbins 
Camera B Operator: Justice Vaughn Ott 
Gaffer: Kevin Kim Best 
Electric: Paul Kane 
Electrics: Noah Shettel, Vahagan Gukasyan, Michael Roseman 
Key Grip: Greg Karamov 
Best Grip: Tyler Johnson-Williams 
Grips: Otis Burkes, Derek Wells 
DIT: Raffaele Vesco 
VTR Operator: Ben Cohen 
Sound Mixer / Playback: John Maynard 
Makeup Artist: Katie Mann 
Colorist: Connor Bailey 
Finishing: Mahyar Mandegar 
Production Assistants: Richard Monteiro, Jadyn Norris Sarno, Sophie Savides 
Set Teacher: Erik Winston 
Set Medic: Gabriel Frolick 
Catering: Beezoo 
Casting: SJ Hasman 
Artist Management: Guy Oseary, Elana Radin 
Video Commissioner: Devin Sarno 
Special Thanks: Cabin Edit, G&J Grip, House Post, Old Fast Glass, Silverlake Conservatory of Music, Walk & Talk 


A PLEA 

(Civil War) 
I hear it in the air  
I feel it in the air  
Who’s your neighbor, who’s your friend?  
Ahh there’s hate all around 

I dont care about your fucking politics  
I don’t wanna hear about your politics  
Well, he said boo  
She said hooray 

Now we are human beings right here  
Human beings We’re here together  

Come on 

Whatcha gonna do? Whatcha gonna do when it falls on you? 

You’re scaring the kids  
The beautiful kids  
Ah yeah they wanna know  
The children wanna know  
Is the ugly coming, and the guns?  
Is the army coming, blotting out the sun?  
The blood red sun, the blood red sun  
Ahhhhhhh concentration camps? 

(Peace and Love) 

My blood runs cold  
I’m feeling hate all around  
It’s no solution  
It’s never been a solution 

Come on Are you with me? 
We all know what it is 

Build a bridge Shine a light 

Make something beautiful  
I don’t care if it’s a little scrap of squiggly crayon on a paper  
Make something beautiful and see somebody  
Give it to somebody  

I’m not being corny this shit is real 

Live for peace Live for love 

It’s all we got 

See the god in everyone  
See the god 

Come on with me 

(The Æther) 

Everyone just wants to be loved  
See the god in everyone  
Everyone leaves out no-one  
And everything besides love is cowardice  
You wanna be brave, you wanna be tough?  
Peace and love is the toughest hardest thing you can do 

Build a bridge that's where the courage is 

Shine your light Shine it true 

Yeah


#Flea #APlea

snippet.title: Minecraft, Mais j'ai Amélioré ma Mine de PAUVRE à RICHE !
snippet.description:
Aujourd'hui, j'ai amélioré mam ine de Pauvre (charbon) à riche de fou ! (un minerai arc-en-ciel carrément je connais pas) pour rendre zinzin mon pote !
Mail pour tout contact commercial : azpaztv@gmail.com
Mon Twitter : https://www.twitter.com/azpaztv
Mon Discord  + de nulcraft : https://discord.gg/EBPCS6YF9e
Merci pour les 700k road to 800k
Ce n'est pas Minecraft, Mais l'eau monte ou Minecraft, mais la lave monte, ou Survivre 100 jours dans Minecraft, ou tout type de défi dans Minecraft mais. Il s'agit d'un speedrun / Manhunt . Shorts ou sur Roblox avec des Brainrot Italien de Steal a brainrot grow a garden ou 99 nuits en forêt c'est des jeux de fou surtout vole un brainrot roblox fr
Dans cette vidéo Minecraft 1.20 (1.21 et non 1.19, 1.18 ou 1.17), je répondrai à toutes les questions que vous me poserez sans faire une seule exception. Il y a des questions embarrassantes, des questions intéressantes et beaucoup d'entre elles tout simplement stupides XD Cette vidéo est l'une de mes préférées que j'ai faites, alors profitez-en :)

Ce n'est pas Minecraft dans la vraie vie, pas l'édition éducative de Minecraft, pas Minecraft, mais en difficulté millionaire de riche. ou alors 7 façons de voler mes amis Cela répond à vos questions les plus litigieuses/absurdes.

Je vous aime tous beaucoup!
